name: Adrian, Texas
description:
in Adrian, Texas, bills itself as geographically the midway point between Los Angeles and Chicago on historic Route 66. Signage in Adrian proudly declares an 1139-mile distance to each original US 66 endpoint. 

Route 66 is one of the essential icons of America, both for Americans and people abroad. It represents many ideas: freedom, migration West, and the loneliness of the American heartland.
